<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ạ̉bạ ạlậb ạ̹lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā ạảbā ạlậbu ại̹laẙka .. biạl̊masīḥi naq̊tarib̊
 biạs̊mihi nad̊nū ladaẙka .. fāl̊ʿaṭāyā tan̊sakib̊

[V2]
 2- man̊ bidamihi gẖusil̊nā .. wabihi lanā salạam̊
 walanā rūḥu ạltãbanĩy ..wasurūruⁿ lildãwām̊

[V3]
 3- kulũnā biạlṭãb̊ʿi kunãạ ..fī ḍalạaliⁿ wāb̊tiʿād̊
 lakini ạlnĩʿ̊maẗu zādat̊ .. faẘqa ại̹tẖ̊miⁿ wafasād̊

[V4]
 4- wabihā faḍ̊lạaⁿ kẖalaṣ̊nā .. mū̊̉minīna biạl̊masīḥ̊
 biạs̊mihi nil̊nā ḥayāẗaⁿ .. ḥas̊ba qaẘlika ạlṣãrīḥ̊</lyrics>
</song>